snippet.title: Spellsworn Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Our Early Access is LIVE! 
This is such an exciting and scary day for the whole team. For over two years we've been working to bring a playable and stable build out for you people to try out. We are tremendously proud and we truly hope you like it! 

Check out our steam page!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/360620/

and social media
www.facebook.com/frogsongstudios
https://twitter.com/FrogsongStudios

We love you all!
/Frogsong Studios
